    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and presents as if it were brand new. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or aging. Every feature functions perfectly, and the mechanical components have been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. This is a rare find for a collector or anyone seeking a vehicle in impeccable, like-new condition.",
