    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all features functioning as intended and only minimal wear on the driver's seat bolster. It runs smoothly and represents a dependable, high-quality option for anyone looking for a solid car without the 'mint' price tag.",
      "price": 34000.0,
